compareMaps(m1, m2) - Static method in class com.mooregreatsoftware.gradle.defaults.UtilsKt
Compares two Maps of Comparable items. If one is null, that sorts lower. If ones size is smaller, that sorts lower. Otherwise the keys are compared. (See .compareSets.) If the keys are the same, the first difference in the values found when searching the sorted keys is used for the comparision.
compareSets(s1, s2) - Static method in class com.mooregreatsoftware.gradle.defaults.UtilsKt
Compares two Sets of Comparable items. If one is null, that sorts lower. If ones size is smaller, that sorts lower. Otherwise the first non-equal value after they are sorted is used for the comparision.
